OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FLast week saw the government announce
OL,8,Fa major climbdown on their planned
OL,9,Fwelfare cuts, after backbench Labour
OL,10,FMPs threatened to block the plans.
OL,12,FThe chancellor will now have to find
OL,13,Fan extra #3bn to fund the u-turn, with
OL,14,Fthe #5bn original savings from the
OL,15,Fplans now only at #2bn.
