OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FPlans to tighten the eligibility
OL,8,Fcriteria for Pip will now only apply
OL,9,Fto future claimants from November
OL,10,F2026, while payments for the health
OL,11,Felement of universal credit will now
OL,12,Frise with inflation for current
OL,13,Fclaimants.
OL,15,FHowever, disability groups and many
OL,16,Fbackbench Labour MPs remain deeply
OL,17,Fconcerned about the impact of the cuts
OL,18,Fon future recipients, warning of a
OL,19,F"two-tier" benefits system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
