OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FOne of the most controversial parts of
OL,8,Fthe package of welfare reforms was the
OL,9,Fplan to tighten eligibility for
OL,10,FPersonal Independence Payments (Pip).
OL,12,FThe government had planned to make it
OL,13,Fmore difficult for people to claim
OL,14,FPip, by raising the the level of
OL,15,Fsupport needed to qualify for the
OL,16,Fpayments. But those changes will now
OL,17,Fonly apply to future claimants after
OL,18,FNovember 2026, while current
OL,19,Frecipients will be protected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
