OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FPeople are assessed for Pip through
OL,8,Fquestions about their ability to do
OL,9,Fdifferent daily tasks independently,
OL,10,Fwith each task scaled on a scale from
OL,11,Fzero to twelve. They currently need to
OL,12,Fscore eight points across the ten
OL,13,Fdifferent categories for the standard
OL,14,Frate, or twelve for the higher rate.
OL,16,FBut from November 2026, new claimants
OL,17,Fwill need to score at least four
OL,18,Fpoints for one activity, rather than a
OL,19,Flower number of points across multiple
OL,20,Factivities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
