OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FThe change in Pip payments is expected
OL,8,Fto exclude some 370,000 existing
OL,9,Fclaimants, who had been expected to
OL,10,Flose out following reassessment.
OL,12,FBut 430,000 future claimants will
OL,13,Fstill be impacted, losing an average
OL,14,Fof #4,500 a year.
OL,16,FAs part of the concessions, the
OL,17,Fgovernment also announced that a
OL,18,Freview into the Pip changes will be
OL,19,F"co-produced" alongside disabled
OL,20,Fpeople, led by Disability Minister
OL,21,FStephen Timms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
