OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FBut, on Monday the government
OL,8,Fconfirmed the review will not conclude
OL,9,Funtil November 2026 - which is when
OL,10,Fthe changes to Pip eligibility for
OL,11,Ffuture claimants are due to come into
OL,12,Feffect.
OL,14,FMany backbench Labour MPs are
OL,15,Fconcerned about the chronology of the
OL,16,Fplans, calling on the government to
OL,17,Fdelay the cuts until the Timms review
OL,18,Fhas reported back.
