OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FWhile the top-up is being cut for new
OL,8,Fclaimants, the basic rate of universal
OL,9,Fcredit will rise from around #92 a
OL,10,Fweek to #106 a week by 2030.
OL,12,FUnder the plans, under-22s will also
OL,13,Fno longer qualify for the health
OL,14,Felement of universal credit.
OL,16,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,17,FKendall has also brought forward plans
OL,18,Fto spend #1bn supporting people back
OL,19,Finto work - the money was due to be
OL,20,Favailable later in the parliament, but
OL,21,Fcan now be spent this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
