OL,3,CWelfare cuts - what changes has the
OL,4,Cgovernment made and will they appease
OL,5,CMPs?
OL,7,FAre the changes enough to persuade MPs
OL,8,Fto support the plans?
OL,10,FThere were 126 MPs who signed an
OL,11,Famendment to block the welfare bill,
OL,12,Fwhich would've been a disaster for the
OL,13,Fgovernment.
OL,15,FOver the weekend it appeared most of
OL,16,Fthe rebels had backed down, but on
OL,17,FMonday afternoon senior MP Debbie
OL,18,FAbrahams told ITV News her group of
OL,19,FMPs was pushing for further
OL,20,Fconcessions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
